9mobile has announced a CashToken Rewards Offer, offered in partnership with CeLD Innovations Limited. The reward programme offers loyal customers on the 9mobile network a chance to win between N5, 000 and N100, 000,000 weekly.
  
The Director, Product Innovation and Business Development, 9mobile, Kenechukwu Okonkwo, who announced the partnership of the reward scheme during a media briefing organised recently, said the programme was part of the company’s commitment to reciprocate the loyalty demonstrated by its customers.
  
“As a brand, 9mobile is always here for our loyal customers, and this is our way of ushering them into the New Year 2023. 